// CORE FLIGHT TECHONOLOGIES ULTRA COMPACT A32X OVERHEAD PANEL firmware for SPAD.neXt SERIAL V2
//
// By 1L2P (Discord 1L2P)
//
// r01 Initial release
//
// Serial com has to be set at 115200 bauds in SPAD serial device settings (default bitrate)
//
// Internal devices features (not designed to be used when connected to SPAD)
// - Cycle backlight brightness by pressing "APU START" and "CALLS ALL" buttons (0, 64 , 128, 192, 255)
// - Soft reset with IR1 set on ATT and by pressing "APU START" and "CALLS ALL" buttons (only use when not connected to SPAD, or just plug/unplug USB cable)
//
// To manage backlight brightness from SPAD, search for these variables.
// - BACKLIGHT_BRI : Panel backlight brightness from 0 to 255 (DEVICE:1L2P/CFTA32XOVHUC/BACKLIGHT_BRI)

// SPAD test snippet for Fly By Wire A32X is #15013
// SPAD test snippet for Fenix A320 is #15012
